Package: org.lenskit.specs

[Java] Interface DynamicSpecHandler

  • Resolve dynamic specifications (pure JSON trees) into objects in an extensible fashion. The heart of this interface is the resolveAndBuild(Class, JsonNode). Instances of this interface are loaded via the java.util.ServiceLoader facility, and queried in turn for one that can turn a particular specification into the requested type. Handlers should be selective in the types they handle, to minimize the chance of conflicts.

    See Also:
    SpecUtils.buildObject
